This projest is test project,
May be later i will use it as a template for my future projects.
For now this project is made from taking reference from, https://dev.to/m_josh/build-a-jwt-login-and-logout-system-using-expressjs-nodejs-hd2

# Steps that I followed.
1. Setting up the development files, installing required packages, and creating a database.
  a. npm init
  b. npm install express mongoose bcrypt cookie-parser dotenv cors express-validator jsonwebtoken
  c. npm install --save-dev nodemon
  d. Create a database on MongoDB
2. Creating Main Route and API server instance
3. Create a server instance for your API
4. Create a user model
5. Create an Input validation
6. Create an authentication controller and routes
